Deployment
Using Docker
bash
# Build the image
docker build -t clinic-dashboard .

# Run the container
docker run -p 3000:3000 clinic-dashboard
Manual Deployment
Build the project: npm run build

Set NODE_ENV=production

Start with process manager: pm2 start server.js

