ğŸ¥ Clinic Management Dashboard
A comprehensive Streamlit-based dashboard for managing clinic operations with real-time analytics and patient management.

Features
ğŸ“Š Dashboard Overview - Key metrics and clinic performance indicators

ğŸ‘¥ Patient Management - Complete patient database with medical records

ğŸ“… Appointment System - Schedule and track patient appointments

ğŸ’Š Medical Records - Digital health records and prescription management

ğŸ“ˆ Analytics - Visual insights with interactive charts and trends

âš ï¸ Alerts - Real-time notifications for today's appointments and stock

Quick Start
Installation
bash
pip install streamlit pandas numpy plotly
Run the Application
bash
streamlit run app.py
Usage
Filter Data - Use sidebar filters to view specific date ranges, doctors, or appointment statuses

View Analytics - Check KPIs and interactive charts for clinic performance

Manage Patients - Access patient records, appointments, and medical history in tabs

Add New Patients - Use the "New Entry" tab to register new patients

Export Data - Download patient and appointment data as CSV files

Data Structure
Patients - 200+ sample patients with demographics and contact info

Doctors - 5 specialists across different medical fields

Appointments - 300+ historical appointments with status tracking

Medical Records - 250+ health records with diagnoses and prescriptions

Key Metrics Tracked
Total patients and appointments

Completed visits and revenue

Today's schedule

Appointment status distribution

Doctor performance

Monthly trends

Technology Stack
Frontend: Streamlit

Data Processing: Pandas, NumPy

Visualization: Plotly

Data: Synthetic clinic data with realistic patterns